{"id":15051,"date":"2026-03-26T14:45:30","date_gmt":"2026-03-26T18:45:30","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/?post_type=evenement&#038;p=15051"},"modified":"2026-03-26T14:57:19","modified_gmt":"2026-03-26T18:57:19","slug":"projection-de-true-north","status":"publish","type":"evenement","link":"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/evenement\/projection-de-true-north\/","title":{"rendered":"Projection de TRUE NORTH"},"content":{"rendered":"<p>En collaboration avec la Vie \u00e9tudiante, les d\u00e9partements de <a href=\"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/programmes\/sciences-humaines\/\">Sciences humaines<\/a> et <a href=\"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/programmes\/cinema-et-communication\/\">Cin\u00e9ma et communication<\/a> pr\u00e9sentent : TRUE NORTH relate les manifestations de 1969 contre le racisme syst\u00e9mique \u00e0 l\u2019Universit\u00e9 Sir George Williams, lorsqu\u2019un groupe d\u2019\u00e9tudiants ha\u00eftiens-canadiens a occup\u00e9 un laboratoire informatique au neuvi\u00e8me \u00e9tage.<\/p>\n<p>Soyez aux premi\u00e8res loges en assistant \u00e0 ce documentaire qui relate la mont\u00e9e d\u2019un mouvement de contestation \u00e0 l\u2019\u00e9chelle continentale \u00e0 la fin des ann\u00e9es\u00a01960. Habilement mise en r\u00e9cit, cette \u0153uvre au montage \u00e9patant est un acte puissant de m\u00e9moire.<\/p>\n<p>Cette activit\u00e9 est pr\u00e9sent\u00e9e dans le cadre de la Semaine d&rsquo;actions contre le racisme.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"featured_media":15052,"template":"","categorieevenement":[193,2489],"etiquette-interne":[2287,2306,2315,2357],"class_list":["post-15051","evenement","type-evenement","status-publish","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","categorieevenement-vie-etudiante","categorieevenement-projection","etiquette-interne-vie-etudiante","etiquette-interne-cinema-et-communication","etiquette-interne-sciences-humaines","etiquette-interne-milieu-de-vie"],"acf":[],"publishpress_future_action":{"enabled":false,"date":"2026-05-05 21